## ğŸš€ Quick Start Guide

### ğŸ“¦ NPM Installation (Recommended)

```bash
# 1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Localacct21/iron-anarchy-minecraft-bot.git
cd iron-anarchy-minecraft-bot

# 2ï¸âƒ£ Install dependencies
npm install

# 3ï¸âƒ£ Setup configuration files
npm run setup

# 4ï¸âƒ£ Start the bot
npm start
```

### ğŸ³ Docker Deployment

```bash
# Pull the latest image
docker pull ghcr.io/localacct21/iron-anarchy-minecraft-bot:latest

# Create configuration directories
mkdir -p config logs

# Setup configuration
npm run setup

# Run in production
docker run -d \
  --name minecraft-bot \
  --restart=unless-stopped \
  -v $(pwd)/config:/app/config:ro \
  -v $(pwd)/logs:/app/logs:rw \
  -p 3000:3000 \
  ghcr.io/localacct21/iron-anarchy-minecraft-bot:latest
```

### âš¡ Quick Commands

```bash
# Available Bot Types
npm start           # ğŸš€ Main bot with all features
npm run basic       # ğŸ® Basic bot with essential plugins
npm run enhanced    # ğŸ”¥ Enhanced bot (if available)

# Testing & Validation
npm test            # ğŸ§ª Run all tests (16/16 passing)
npm run test:startup # ğŸ” Validate installation
```

